WebSocketClientFactory
public class NettyWebSocketClientFactory
extends Object
implements WebSocketClientFactory

A factory for creating Websocket clients. The entry point for creating and connecting a client. Can and should be used to create multiple instances. Extended for Websocket client request methods.
